title: Behind the Rhetoric: Debunking RFK Jr.
description:

title: Swing Left WA - Book Club: On Tyranny by Timothy Snyder
description:
If you haven't heard about it, _On Tyranny: Twenty Lessons from the Twentieth Century_ is a book published in 2017 by Timothy Snyder, a historian of 20th-century Europe. Rachel Maddow has repeatedly brought him back to her show to explain how to make sense of the current moment. ([Here is a recent appearance](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nNrbInmlHhA)). This book is more relevant than ever. Many of the warnings in the books are being played out in front of our eyes right now. So it's important to know how to recognize these signs, and more importantly, what we could learn from history and do differently this time. 

The book is fairly short, only 126 pages. It would take just an afternoon to finish. If you need to purchase a copy, consider buying from a local bookstore.

Bonus, Stacey Abrams is also doing a book club with this book on her [podcast](https://crooked.com/podcast-series/assemblyrequired/). So once you finish it, you can jump there and learn more insights from her.
